msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:774
msgid ""
"Starting from CUDA 9.0, Nvidia provides minimal CUDA images based on Ubuntu. "
"Please see `their instructions <https://hub.docker.com/r/nvidia/cuda/>`_. "
